<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Apiaceae" genus="Caucalis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Apiales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="395">Caucalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, as do the associated Burser material and cited Colonna element. The name may be in need of conservation with a conserved type.
</paragraph>
